OL,3,CReports of black oil in River Wye as
OL,4,C'suspected pollution' investigated
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency is investing
OL,7,Fthe source of a "suspected pollution"
OL,8,Fin the River Wye in Hereford.
OL,10,FLocals have told ITV News Central that
OL,11,Fthey spotted what appears to be black
OL,12,Foil in the river at midday on Saturday
OL,13,F28 December.
OL,15,FThey said that Environment Agency
OL,16,Fofficers attended the scene near the
OL,17,FHolme Lacy Bridge on Saturday
OL,18,Fafternoon.
