OL,6,FRobert Fox from the Old Harp Fishery
OL,7,Fnear Ross-on-Wye said he fears for the
OL,8,Fimpact of the suspected spill on
OL,9,Fwildlife.
OL,11,FHe added: "This is yet another threat,
OL,12,Fparticularly to water birds and to the
OL,13,Friver banks."
OL,15,FThe Environment Agency said:
OL,16,F"Following a report of a suspected
OL,17,Fpollution into the River Wye in
OL,18,FHereford, our officers are currently
OL,19,Finvestigating the source."
