OL,3,CReports of black oil in River Wye as
OL,4,C'suspected pollution' investigated
OL,6,FITV News Central has contacted
OL,7,FHerefordshire County Council for a
OL,8,Fresponse.
OL,10,FAn investigation by ITV Central in May
OL,11,F2021 found some rivers in the Midlands
OL,12,Fwere carrying up to 50 times the safe
OL,13,Flevel of chemicals in the water.
OL,15,FIn September 2022, we revealed that in
OL,16,F2020 alone, 33 years worth of sewage
OL,17,Fwas dumped into the catchment area of
OL,18,Fthe River Wye, which runs through
OL,19,FHerefordshire.
